    <item>
        <title>Getting Started with Versana: Your Complete WordPress FSE Theme Setup Guide</title>
        <link>https://versana.codoplex.com/blog/getting-started-versana-wordpress-theme</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
        <wp:post_id>7</wp:post_id>
        <wp:post_date>2026-03-04 09:00:00</wp:post_date>
        <wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
        <wp:status>publish</wp:status>
        <wp:post_name>getting-started-versana-wordpress-theme</wp:post_name>
        <category domain="post_tag" nicename="block-theme">block theme</category>
		<category domain="post_tag" nicename="fse-theme">fse theme</category>
		<category domain="category" nicename="getting-started">Getting Started</category>
		<category domain="category" nicename="tutorials">Tutorials</category>
		<category domain="post_tag" nicename="versana-theme">versana theme</category>
		<category domain="post_tag" nicename="wordpress-setup">wordpress setup</category>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Learn how to set up Versana WordPress theme in minutes. Complete guide to installation, demo import, and customization for your FSE website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Welcome to Versana: Your Modern WordPress Theme</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Congratulations on choosing Versana! You've just installed one of the most powerful and user-friendly Full Site Editing (FSE) themes available for WordPress. Whether you're building a blog, business website, or creative portfolio, Versana gives you everything you need to create a stunning website in minutes.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In this guide, we'll walk you through everything you need to know to get started with Versana, from initial setup to customizing your first page.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What Makes Versana Different?</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Before we dive into setup, let's quickly cover what makes Versana special:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Pure WordPress, No Page Builders</strong>: Versana uses WordPress's native Full Site Editing system. This means faster performance, better security, and no vendor lock-in.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>16 Professional Block Patterns</strong>: Pre-designed sections for heroes, features, testimonials, pricing tables, and more. Just insert and customize.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:buttons -->
<div class="wp-block-buttons"><!-- wp:button -->
<div class="wp-block-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button" href="https://versana.codoplex.com/blog/getting-started-versana-wordpress-theme/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Read More</a></div>
<!-- /wp:button --></div>
<!-- /wp:buttons -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Learn how to set up Versana WordPress theme in minutes. Complete guide to installation, demo import, and customization for your FSE website.]]></excerpt:encoded>
    </item>

