        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Learn to optimize Versana theme for maximum performance. Built-in lazy loading, lightweight code, and speed best practices. No extra plugins needed.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Why Performance Matters</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Your website's loading speed affects everything:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>User Experience</strong>: 53% of visitors leave if a page takes longer than 3 seconds to load.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>SEO Rankings</strong>: Google considers page speed a ranking factor. Faster sites rank higher.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Conversions</strong>: A 1-second delay in page load can reduce conversions by 7%.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Mobile Users</strong>: Mobile users are even less patient. Speed is critical for mobile traffic.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The good news? Versana is built for speed from the ground up. With a few simple optimizations, you can achieve 90+ PageSpeed scores easily.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

